- **Framework**: React 19.2.0 with TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: Vite 7.2.1
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4.1.17 + custom font-face declarations
- **Animation**: GSAP 3.13.0 via `@gsap/react` helpers
