- `npm run build`: Build for production
- `npm run build:staging`: Production build using the staging mode flag
- `npm run lint`: Run ESLint
- `npm run preview`: Preview production build

## Additional directories

- **`src/hooks/`**: Contains reusable logic such as `useViewportHeight` (CSS custom property syncing) and `useSiteNavigationController` (global navigation state powered by Zustand).
- **`public/images/`**: Houses static image assets, currently the exported logo used by UI atoms.
- **`src/components/ui/organisms/HeroSlider/`**: Complex hero carousel composed of supporting molecules (titles, progress, indicators) and animations orchestrated via GSAP helpers in `animations.ts`.
